      <title>地缘政治风险加剧加剧供应担忧，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-rise-heightened-geopolitical-risk-exacerbates-supply-concern-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一亚洲早盘，油价上涨，原因是对中东以及俄罗斯和乌克兰冲突升级导致全球供应紧张的担忧，而美国钻机数量减少也加剧了油价上行压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-rise-heightened-geopolitical-risk-exacerbates-supply-concern-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 00:59:08 GMT</pubDate>
